responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "252CADE1473FB0E6386DEAAFEEAAA1D6", "P.19.Month and Day: This will be my last entry. I have discovered a great betrayal and judgement was passed. I have instructed the Sods on what must be done and they can retain the estate as long as the guards or bandits allow. I must go. Not from this region or continents, but from this existence. Blood has been spilled and if there was never a curse upon the Daragal, there is now. Farewell.")
